data.description: Gated Community, Two Story on curve, Leo brick with stone accents, 6 bedrooms with 4 Baths and 3 car garage with plenty of drive way parking. Two bedrooms at first level with en-suite baths. Gourmet Kitchen is open to Family Room with generous quartz island with bar seating, maple cabinets and farmhouse sink! Soaring Ceilings, floor to ceiling windows, light and bright! At second level are 4 bedrooms and game room. Covered Patio for entertaining!
